Jefferson, towards the end of the book, you imagine Lewis is home and he's got his map.

53:32.456 --> 53:36.199
And Jefferson is falling on the wall.

53:36.559 --> 53:38.922
Isn't that scene wonderful?

53:38.942 --> 53:41.444
That is such a wonderful, wonderful scene.

53:41.564 --> 53:42.805
Jefferson is waiting.

53:42.785 --> 54:04.843
