54:05.161 --> 54:09.088
If they didn't say anything, I don't use it.

54:09.148 --> 54:11.452
I mean, it's what they said.

54:11.613 --> 54:17.644
So let's see where Jefferson is on his knees going over the chart prepared by Lewis.

54:18.846 --> 54:21.250
This is based on Jefferson's own testimony.

54:21.411 --> 54:22.893
Yeah, exactly.

54:22.913 --> 54:23.414
Exactly.

